data.description: Check out this beautiful home in Olentangy Schools and the Woods of Olentangy community! Featuring 4 beds, 3.5 baths, finished basement (w/full bath), fenced yard, large patio, renovated kitchen (w/quartz counters, black stainless steel appliances, composite sink), and much more.  With 2,216 sf total and a large outdoor area, you will have lots of space to live, entertain friends and family, and grow into the future!  Recent updates include: A/C & furnace (2018/19), kitchen renovation (2021), carpet with pet guard and upgraded pad (2023), and paver patio (2016). Located extremely close to schools, parks, highways, dining, shopping, Polaris Mall, and medical facilities.  Check this one out today!
